idel = [[\textbf{Idel} - idle \phnm{/ˈʌɪd(ə)l/ (adj.)}: OE \textit{idel} ``empty, void; vain; worthless, useless,'' from Proto-West Germanic *\textit{idla}- (source also of OS \textit{idal}, OF \textit{idel} ``empty, worthless,'' Old Dutch \textit{idil}, OHG \textit{ital}, German \textit{eitel} ``vain, useless, mere, pure''), a word of unknown origin.]]

