nought = [[\textbf{Nouȝt} - nought \phnm{/nɔːt/ (n.)}: Archaic. Nothing. From OE \textit{nowiht} ``nothing,'' variant of \textit{nawiht}. Meaning ``zero, cipher'' is from early 15c.]]

